Title: Oral-B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush
Description: Constant use of electric toothbrushes prevents tooth and gum diseases and helps improve your overall oral health. Packed with beneficial features and advanced technologies, the Oral B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush reaches even the hardest dental regions to perform a powerful and efficient tooth cleaning. In order to ensure smooth and easy brushing, this toothbrush is equipped with an ergonomic ultra-thin soft rubber grip handle, making it effortless to reach even the tough inter-dental regions. Adding to the brushing convenience, this Oral B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush also comprises of a rotating power head that loosens and whisks away plaque from the surface of your teeth, gum lines and back teeth. For an efficient and germ-free tooth cleaning, all you need to do is apply some paste on the brush head, place the brush in your mouth, simply slide the power button on and watch the way your teeth get cleaner, whiter and healthier every passing day. This innovative Oral B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush runs on replaceable AA Alkaline Battery. Performance Made for convenience, the Oral B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush is integrated with a waterproof body, allowing for hassle-free everyday handling. Besides this, the brush replacement indicator signals you when it is time to replace your brush head and is hence simple-to-use. Assisting you in maintaining a good dental routine, this Oral B CrossAction Power Electric Toothbrush is an ideal choice for all those who crave for a wider and healthier smile.
